          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客官，我有一徒弟，此人性如烈火。若他来时，不要睬他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是，我记下了，师父请便。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老僧下。杨延昭哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，爹爹呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延昭睡，杨五郎带酒上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘿，好酒，好酒！吃的来好不爽快也！呣……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（新水令） 归来余醉未曾醒，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "撞着俺五爷爷无些干净。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呜呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（新水令） 莫不是山中老树怪，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫不是潭底毒龙精。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只俺这道高的鬼神敬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（驻马听） 只听得噎噎哽哽，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "搅乱俺，无是无非廊下僧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延昭哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨延德 （驻马听） 呜他，他哭的孤苦伶仃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫不是着枪带箭，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "靠三门倚定价壁儿听"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "耸双肩手抵着牙儿定"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（驻马听） 那些败残兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀爹爹呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（驻马听） 叫的俺沸沸腾腾，沸沸腾腾，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看绿荫满地禅房静。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是山门，呔，开门来，开门来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老僧上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "老僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想是徒弟回来了，待我与你开门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨五郎进门，吐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，哪里吃的这般大醉回来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父，弟子未曾吃酒，山下那些烧刀子烂狗肉的，啊……吃的倒也爽快。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那些腌臜东西，岂是你我出家人用的！罪过，罪过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "弟子改过。师父，什么人在这里啼哭？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没有人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徒弟上山来，明明听得有人在此啼哭，怎么说没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你听见了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听见了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有一远方来的客官，只因天色已晚，在此借住一宿，明日早行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这样来路不明之人，留他做甚！待我打发他出去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了。你不要生事，不要闯祸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父，徒弟不生事，不闯祸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，来，来，与我安歇了吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！这等唠唠叼叼的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿弥陀佛。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老僧下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈……这等样来路不明之人，留他做甚。待我打发他出去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂！那汉子醒来，你是哪里来的？喂，那汉子醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延昭醒，拔剑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看剑！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱家不生事，咱不闯祸。收拾了你这个买卖吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个莽撞和尚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个狠汉子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那汉子，你是哪里来的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是来处来的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你往哪里去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我要往去处去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（步步娇） 莫不是负屈衔冤，恁可也通名姓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫不是，远方来，探望你那爹娘病。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨延德 （步步娇） 莫不是犯法违条，你的罪不轻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺也不犯谁的法。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨延德 （步步娇） 莫不是打担推车，恁撞着那伙贼兵，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那伙贼兵也不是俺的对手！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（步步娇） 俺这里，连问你那两三声，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恁那里，并无有半句话儿来答应。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺不答应你便怎样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺这里厉害！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "厉害，你敢打人骂人不成？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（雁儿落） 俺这里，便打了人，也无争竞，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢骂人吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨延德 （雁儿落） 俺这里便骂了人也不回应。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢劫人吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨延德 （雁儿落） 俺这里便劫了人也无个罪名，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢杀人吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨延德 （雁儿落） 俺这里便杀了人也不偿命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你说便这等说，我是不信的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（水仙子） 烟腾腾火烧人肉喷鼻腥，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可不道为惜飞蛾罩灯？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨延德 （水仙子） 哪里管惜飞蛾纱罩灯！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "念几声观自在超度他的经。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想你也不是自幼出家。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨延德 （水仙子） 吓呀客官吓，细说个分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自幼年间，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（水仙子） 曾杀的番兵怕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客官，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（水仙子） 几时儿有信士请？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到中年落发，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（水仙子） 在此为僧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听他之言，倒是一个好和尚。待俺对他说了吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那和尚，俺是大宋来的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么讲？你是大宋来的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺要盘你一盘？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你盘俺哪一家？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是那大……大……大……大宋！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（雁儿落） 有一个使金刀杨令公他手段能，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他家还有何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨延德 （雁儿落） 他家有七个儿子心肠硬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨延德 （雁儿落） 母亲是佘太君，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敕赐的天波楼无邪佞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他弟兄们可都有哩？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨延德 （雁儿落） 啊呀客官吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只俺在五台山又为僧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还有何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨延德 （雁儿落） 还有个六郎镇守在三关上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可认得他哩？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客官。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（雁儿落） 咱和他一爹娘亲弟兄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听他之言，好象我五郎哥哥。是也不是，我应他一声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那和尚，你敢是我五郎哥哥？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小弟延昭在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨延德 （得胜令） 吓呀贤弟呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相逢，这会合真侥幸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉母亲之命，到幽州昊天塔上盗取爹爹骨殖而回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹骨殖在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在这里。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在哪里，哇呀……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延德接匣悲。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨延德 （得胜令） 呜呀爹爹呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好伤情。把幽魂陷虏城把幽魂陷虏城。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延德跪拜。番兵内追喊。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥，番兵追来，如何是好！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟，你在后面，咱一同打发他回去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延德、杨延昭同下。萧天佐上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧天佐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧天佐",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我做大将胆子大，出战发兵我不怕。忽听大炮一声响，吓得我八天没说话。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧天佐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺萧天佐。奉太后密旨，追赶南蛮盗骨之人，追到此处不见了。来此已是五台"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧天佐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "山，想必藏在这里，待我下马问问和尚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧天佐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！和尚开门来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延德上，开门。杨延德、萧天佐对打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（川拨棹） 这厮呵待蒙挣，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那厮呵待蒙挣。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待杀官兵，扑杀苍蝇。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我打，打你个小头也那官兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我打！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（七弟兄） 这厮呵带鞓，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "摔你个满天星。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（萧天佐跪架铲。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧天佐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们出家人连个慈悲心也没有吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咦，哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（七弟兄） 哎休，休道俺出家人并无个慈悲性，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怒轰轰恶向胆边生。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恁且来、来、来，好好还俺杨令公爹爹命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延德杀萧天佐，萧天佐下。杨延昭上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "番兵已退，哥哥随小弟回家见母亲一面。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟，俺既出了家，还回家做甚？贤弟与我多多拜上老母便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延昭允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟请乘骑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待愚兄步送一程者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（清江引） 番兵个个皆逃遁，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "死在俺手中。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方显得老杨家有后生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！你们谁敢来，你们谁敢来呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延德、杨延昭同下。）"
        }
      ],
